                                   ||
                    this name we should give as the file which we download
  
    ->>  to verify    
            []$ ls -lrt
        now you the the file which is untar .
    -->> now follow the steps from step3 in the above link  (https://jhooq.com/prometheous-grafan-setup/)


 --->> while we run the command      []$ ./prometheus      /// then it will open temporarly whiloe we using   ctrl + c
 then it will stop 

--->>> for open permanently use this command  


         []$ nohup ./prometheus --config.file=prometheus.yml > prometheus.log 2>&1 &



 ---... explantion
              nohup: runs the command immune to hangups (terminal exit).

             > prometheus.log 2>&1: logs output to prometheus.log.

            &: puts the process in the background.

             âœ… Prometheus will keep running even after you close the terminal.

